flowchart TD
    A[Folder 7 output<br/>seeded SourcePlanner queue] --> B[runPlannerQueueSnapshotPhase]
    B --> C[runFetcherStartPhase]
    C --> D{fetcher.start ok?}
    D -->|yes| E[base fetcher ready]
    D -->|no and not dryrun/http| F[fallback to HttpFetcher.start]
    F --> E
    E --> G[createModeAwareFetcherRegistry]
    G --> H[runProcessPlannerQueuePhase]

    H --> I{fetchSchedulerEnabled}
    I -->|true| J[runFetchSchedulerDrain]
    I -->|false| K[direct while planner.hasNext]

    J --> L[runSourcePreflightPhase]
    K --> L

    L --> M{preflight.mode}
    M -->|skip| L
    M -->|stop| Z[stop queue drain]
    M -->|process| N[preflight payload<br/>source + sourceHost + hostBudgetRow]

    N --> O{runSourceSkipBeforeFetchPhase}
    O -->|runtime blocked domain| L
    O -->|frontier cooldown| L
    O -->|host budget blocked/backoff| L
    O -->|fetch allowed| P[runSourceFetchDispatchPhase]

    P --> Q[assign workerId fetch-N]
    Q --> R[runSourceFetchPhase]
    R --> S[resolve requested mode<br/>override -> discovery/http -> static/http -> requires_js/playwright -> base mode]
    S --> T[host concurrency gate + wrapper retry]
    T --> U[fetcher.fetch or registry.fetchWithMode]
    U --> V[inner fetcher builds pageData<br/>robots + pacing + throttling + navigation + capture]

    V --> W{fetch ok?}
    W -->|no| X[classify failure<br/>host budget/backoff<br/>frontier record<br/>repair handoff<br/>trace write]
    X --> Y[scheduler may retry or switch modes<br/>otherwise continue queue]
    Y --> L

    W -->|yes| AA[sourceFetch<br/>ok + pageData + fetchDurationMs + fetcherModeUsed]
    AA --> AB[runSourceProcessingPhase]
    AB --> AC[Folder 9 begins]

    classDef phase fill:#eef6ff,stroke:#245b99,color:#0f172a
    classDef outcome fill:#f5f5f5,stroke:#666,color:#111
    classDef handoff fill:#ecfdf3,stroke:#1f7a45,color:#0f172a

    class B,C,G,H,J,K,L,N,P,Q,R,S,T,U,V phase
    class X,Y,Z outcome
    class AA,AB,AC handoff
